data.description: Stunning! Nestled in the desirable and quaint community of Calhoun, this stunning 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home on 151 Orchard Way SE offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and comfortable living. Boasting an open floor plan with high vaulted ceilings and abundant natural light, this home is ideal for entertaining and everyday living. The spacious living area features a cozy fireplace and hardwood floors, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The updated kitchen is a chef's dream with stainless steel appliances and ample storage space. The Owner's Suite has been beautifully updated and includes a separate tub and shower. With an additional flex room (5th bedroom) and finished basement, there is plenty of space for an office, gym, or playroom. This move-in ready home also offers central AC and heating for year-round comfort. Enjoy picturesque views from the private backyard, elevated deck, perfect for outdoor gatherings. Situated on a large privacy fenced lot with a wooded backdrop, this property offers a quiet and serene setting. Located in a top-rated school district and close to highways, this home provides easy access to all the amenities of Calhoun and I-75 while still maintaining a peaceful community feel. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home. Schedule a showing today!
